title: Don't Delay, Apply Today!!!
posting_body: ['New 2021 Home!!!', 'Groveland Manor welcomes all newcomers and current residents with warmth and respect from our professionally managed and beautifully maintained community.', 'Our gorgeous country setting provides for a quiet and active lifestyle.', 'We offer a pool, basketball court, playground, dog walk area, boat/RV storage, and community clubhouse for hosting community events.', 'This beautiful brand new 2021 home comes equipped with all black appliances (refrigerator, stove/oven, microwave/ hood vent, dishwasher, and garbage disposal).', 'Fresh paint, flooring, and COVID sanitized.', 'Your own private yard to build a snowman, put up seasonal decorations, and a storage shed!', 'Loads of cabinet space in a spacious kitchen to cook up homemade meals.', 'The safety and security of your own private entrance to your home, no shared walls, and open-air space provides for your family to live a well-balanced socially distant life.', 'This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.', 'In-unit laundry ~ no lugging baskets to the laundry mat!', 'On and Off-street parking as well as overflow parking areas for when you have guests.', 'Here at Yes Communities and Groveland Manor we pride ourselves on offering Gold Key Services (Preventative/Routine/Emergency Services).', 'Call Groveland Manor today at:', 'show contact info', '!']
